Package net.mtrop.doom.struct.io

Class JSPISoundHandle

java.lang.Object
net.mtrop.doom.struct.io.JSPISoundHandle
public class JSPISoundHandle
extends Object
Sound resource abstraction. Wraps Java Sound SPI structures for ease of creating handles to decodable sound.
Author:
Matthew Tropiano
